get alignment length¶

In [2]:
LengthAlignment = {'Arc': {}, 'Bac': {}, 'Euk': {},
         'ArcBac': {}, 'ArcEuk': {}, 'BacEuk': {},
         'ArcBacEuk': {}}

for grp in LengthAlignment:
    files = subprocess.check_output("ls /home/anais/Documents/Projet/G4Evolution/gapFam/"+grp+"/", shell=True)
    files = files.decode("utf-8")
    files = files[:-1]
    for file in files.split('\n'):
        tree = file.split('.')[0]
        nbLines = subprocess.check_output("cat /home/anais/Documents/Projet/G4Evolution/ProcessedAlign/ProcAlignment_"+tree+".csv", shell=True)
        nbLines = nbLines.decode("utf-8")
        LengthAlignment[grp][tree] = len(nbLines.split('\n')) -1

get up/down stream coord¶

In [3]:
grpSp = {'Arc': {}, 'Bac': {}, 'Euk': {},
         'ArcBac': {}, 'ArcEuk': {}, 'BacEuk': {},
         'ArcBacEuk': {}}

for grp in grpSp:
    files = subprocess.check_output("ls /home/anais/Documents/Projet/G4Evolution/gapFam/"+grp+"/", shell=True)
    files = files.decode("utf-8")[:-1]
    for file in files.split('\n'):
        tree = file.split('.')[0]
        grpSp[grp][tree] = {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []}
        content = subprocess.check_output('cat /home/anais/Documents/Projet/G4Evolution/mergedpG4FamiliesTestPer/'+tree+'.csv', shell=True)
        content = content.decode("utf-8").split('\n')[1:-1]
        for fam in content:
            fam = fam.split('\t')
            grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'].append([ int(fam[1]), int(fam[2]) ])
        for i in range(0, len(grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'])):
            lenFam = float(grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]-grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]+1)
            if i != 0 and i != len(grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'])-1:
                #not the first or last fam
                start =  grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1]+1
                end = grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-1
                grpSp[grp][tree]['Rest'].append([start, end])
                if not grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i+1][0] < grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+300:
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Down'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+1, grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+300])
                else:
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Down'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+1, grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i+1][0]])
                if not grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1] > grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300:
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300, end])
                else:
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1], end])
            elif i == 0 and grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0] == 0:
                #first fam and start at the begining of the alignment
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Down'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+1, grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+300])
            elif i == 0 and grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0] != 0:
                #first fam and do not start at the begining of the alignment
                start =  0
                end = grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-1
                grpSp[grp][tree]['Rest'].append([start, end])
                if len(grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam']) != 1:
                    if not grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i+1][0] < grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+300:
                        grpSp[grp][tree]['Down'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+1, grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+300])
                    else:
                        grpSp[grp][tree]['Down'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+1, grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i+1][0]])
                    if not grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1] > grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300:
                        grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300, end])
                    else:
                        grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1], end])
                else:
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Down'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+1, grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+300])
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300, end])
            elif i == len(grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'])-1 and grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1] == LengthAlignment[grp][tree]:
                #last fam and end at the end of the alignment
                start =  grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1]+1
                end = grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-1
                grpSp[grp][tree]['Rest'].append([start, end])
                if len(grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam']) != 1:
                    if not grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1] > grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300:
                        grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300, end])
                    else:
                        grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1], end])
                else:
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300, end])
            elif i == len(grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'])-1 and grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1] != LengthAlignment[grp][tree]:
                #last fam and do not end at the end of the alignment
                start =  grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]
                end = LengthAlignment[grp][tree]
                grpSp[grp][tree]['Rest'].append([start, end])
                if len(grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam']) > 1:
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Down'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+1, grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+300])
                    if not grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1] > grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300:
                        grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300, end])
                    else:
                        grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i-1][1], end])
                else:
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Down'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+1, grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][1]+300])
                    grpSp[grp][tree]['Up'].append([grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam'][i][0]-300, end])

statConservation = {'Arc': {'Entropy': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'Identity': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'RatioSeq': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []}},
                    'Bac': {'Entropy': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'Identity': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'RatioSeq': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []}},
                    'Euk': {'Entropy': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'Identity': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'RatioSeq': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []}},
                    'ArcBac': {'Entropy': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'Identity': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'RatioSeq': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []}},
                    'ArcEuk': {'Entropy': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'Identity': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'RatioSeq': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []}},
                    'BacEuk': {'Entropy': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'Identity': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'RatioSeq': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []}},
                    'ArcBacEuk': {'Entropy': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'Identity': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []},
                           'RatioSeq': {'Fam': [], 'Up': [], 'Down': [], 'Rest': []}}}

for grp in grpSp:
    for tree in grpSp[grp]:
        df = pd.read_csv('/home/anais/Documents/Projet/G4Evolution/ProcessedAlign/ProcAlignment_'+tree+'.csv', sep='\t')
        for f in grpSp[grp][tree]['Fam']:
            statConservation[grp]['Entropy']['Fam'].append(df['Entropy'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
            statConservation[grp]['Identity']['Fam'].append(df['Identiy'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
            statConservation[grp]['RatioSeq']['Fam'].append(df['RatioSeq'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
        for f in grpSp[grp][tree]['Up']:
            statConservation[grp]['Entropy']['Up'].append(df['Entropy'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
            statConservation[grp]['Identity']['Up'].append(df['Identiy'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
            statConservation[grp]['RatioSeq']['Up'].append(df['RatioSeq'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
        for f in grpSp[grp][tree]['Down']:
            statConservation[grp]['Entropy']['Down'].append(df['Entropy'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
            statConservation[grp]['Identity']['Down'].append(df['Identiy'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
            statConservation[grp]['RatioSeq']['Down'].append(df['RatioSeq'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
        for f in grpSp[grp][tree]['Rest']:
            statConservation[grp]['Entropy']['Rest'].append(df['Entropy'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
            statConservation[grp]['Identity']['Rest'].append(df['Identiy'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())
            statConservation[grp]['RatioSeq']['Rest'].append(df['RatioSeq'][f[0]:f[1]].mean())

    print(grp)
    for measure in statConservation[grp]:
        print(measure)
        if measure == 'Entropy':
            sns.boxplot(data=statConservation[grp][measure]['Fam'], color="#3f7e90")
            plt.ylim(0,2.4)
            plt.show()

            plt.ylim(0,2.4)
